casebody.data:
Scott VALENTINE, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Maximo ALMANZAR and Ana Almanzar, Defendants-Respondents. C-238 September Term 2017
079685 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 26, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002207-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
